data.description: Discover tranquility in this inviting 55+ community home nestled in a serene and quiet area.  Boasting newer windows that flood the interiors with natural night, this residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality.  The spacious backyard provides an ideal retreat, perfect for gardening, relaxation, or entertaining guests.  Embrace a lifestyle of ease with the convenience of single-story living, ensuring accessibility for all.  Whether you're enjoying the peaceful surroundings or socializing with neighbors, this home provides a haven for those seeking a harmonious blend of comfort and community in a picturesque and quiet 55+ setting.
